{"tid":1247214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以南北韓式大喇叭向當值緊既警務人員發放多角度資訊","createTime":"2019-06-21T04:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:36:36.000Z","uid":263331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1dfa17cb2322f5b1ef56dbc8274280a27e61c8","tid":1247214,"uid":263331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7rdbMy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7rdbMy.jpg&h=5a4aca73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實警方群組係唔會互傳黑警打人/違法/一哥割蓆，只會傳CCTVB「暴民」遍段. <br />\n<br />\n如果效法南韓向北韓播少時咁，有冇得諗？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無間段式</span></strong>向當值緊既警務人員<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發放多角度新聞/警例/李明逵講話/建制派既謊話/濫用私刑後果</span></strong>等等！<br />\n<br />\n合法、反單向洗腦教育、既和平又理性！<br />\n注意要符合：合理音量或其他合法條件<br />\n<br />\n參考資料<br />\n1。拆解南北韓的擴音器對決<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/674399/史檔：拆解南北韓的擴音器對決\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F674399%2F%E5%8F%B2%E6%AA%94%EF%BC%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E7%9A%84%E6%93%B4%E9%9F%B3%E5%99%A8%E5%B0%8D%E6%B1%BA&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=afb4829e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/674399/史檔：拆解南北韓的擴音器對決</a><br />\n2。美軍空投傳單 圖示ISIS將新成員丟入絞肉機 <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20150327/s00005/1427423726676/美軍空投傳單-圖示isis將新成員丟入絞肉機\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20150327%2Fs00005%2F1427423726676%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%95%E5%82%B3%E5%96%AE-%E5%9C%96%E7%A4%BAisis%E5%B0%87%E6%96%B0%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%9F%E5%85%A5%E7%B5%9E%E8%82%89%E6%A9%9F&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=bee100d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20150327%2Fs00005%2F1427423726676%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%95%E5%